<p class="">I certainly think that the right hon. Gentleman has gone rather wide. The real discussion is as to the rate of 20 and 22 per cent. or the other figures mentioned in the Amendments, but I was hoping that perhaps if I permitted him a little latitude it might avoid any debate on the more general Question that the Clause stand part.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
