<p class="">The hon. Gentleman says that this is a Profits Tax <span id="1258" class="column-number" data-column-number="1258"></span> upon profits. Does not that depend on how profits are defined, and has not the Chancellor himself already recognised the fact that the present definition of profits is wholly misleading?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
