        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. Member referred to the Profits Tax Act. I take it that what he has in mind is the Finance Act.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6d4ea843-3c5a-4d1d-8d35-ef8a9d500b01" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-11-09/debates/3a59af49-9c14-4b01-82c5-a07dd977c336/Clause1%E2%80%94(RatesOfTaxEtc)#contribution-6d4ea843-3c5a-4d1d-8d35-ef8a9d500b01">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
